(1333, 3, '2016-07-15 18:13:43', '2016-07-15 18:13:43', '<img class="wp-image-1386 alignleft" title="Coolpad Snow Day in Miami " src="http://res.cloudinary.com/coolpad/image/upload/c_scale,q_60,w_1200/v1474275896/IMG_20160813_104724_qpjhr3.jpg" alt="32 tons of snow " width="472" height="317" />\r\n\r\nOn one hot summer day in Miami, FL snow came to town. Yup, snow, 32 tons of it! What better way of introducing our brand to the US market? Our smartphones are already known in many parts of the world but like they say, first impressions always matter, let’s just say it really mattered to us. We hosted this great event were around *** people attending. Bringing snow to Miami did bring us lots of great stories and great experiences. One girl came up to me asking if this is how actual snow feels like. Now that definitely put a smile on my face, giving someone the cool opportunity to play with snow for the first time. Not only that but to bring it to Miami, one of the hottest cities in the country! Let’s just say we had a blast hosting this amazing event, showing off our cool smartphones as well as our smart watches and Coolpad VRs. To see more of the event check out our video! We hope to bring more fun for you all, stay tuned and stay cool for life!\r\n\r\nTV station show up and interviewed Coolpad executives regarding this initiative.', 'Coolpad Snow Day in Miami', '', 'draft', 'open', 'closed', '', 'coolpad-snow-day-in-miami', '', '', '2016-09-19 05:31:19', '2016-09-19 13:31:19', '', 0, 'http://localhost/coolpad/?p=1333', 0, 'post', '', 0),
