(1367, 3, '2016-07-29 21:35:10', '2016-07-29 21:35:10', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_single_image source="external_link" alignment="center" custom_src="http://res.cloudinary.com/coolpad/image/upload/v1469827462/banner_zdomkp.jpg"][vc_row_inner css=".vc_custom_1469944426344{padding-right: 15% !important;padding-left: 15% !important;}"][vc_column_inner el_class="content"][vc_custom_heading text="Get Ready Miami - you\'re getting 32 tons of snow on Saturday, August 13th " font_container="tag:h2|font_size:48|text_align:center|color:%233b3fb6" google_fonts="font_family:Lato%3A100%2C100italic%2C300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal"][vc_column_text]That’s right, Coolpad Americas is taking America by storm—snow storm. And all starts in Miami with the official U.S. launch of Coolpad, the most affordable, full-featured smartphones in the U.S., and ranked in the top ten smartphones worldwide. So, come check out the phones. Sled some slopes. Play in the snow. And show your support for the Children’s Miracle Network. <strong>It’s all free. </strong>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_custom_1470000614989{margin-top: 3em !important;margin-bottom: 3em !important;padding-right: 15% !important;padding-left: 15% !important;}"][vc_column width="1/3" css=".vc_custom_1470000624401{margin-top: 2em !important;margin-bottom: 2em !important;}"][vc_column_text]<strong>Special Thanks to</strong> <img src="http://res.cloudinary.com/coolpad/image/upload/v1469827981/BAYSIDE_LOGO2_i8oi07.jpg" width="200px" />[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3" css=".vc_custom_1470000636632{margin-top: 2em !important;margin-bottom: 2em !important;}"][vc_column_text]<strong>Proudly supporting</strong> <img src="http://res.cloudinary.com/coolpad/image/upload/c_scale,h_88/v1469827980/children_smiraclenetwork_kw7dxf.jpg" width="200px" />[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="