(1417, 2, '2016-12-23 15:16:02', '2016-12-23 23:16:02', '[vc_row el_id="in-page-nav"][vc_column width="1/2" el_class="information"][vc_column_text el_class="phone"]coolpad <strong>conjr</strong>[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text el_class="price"]from $[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" el_class="nav-links"][vc_raw_html][/vc_raw_html][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row content_placement="middle" el_id="product-cover-hero" el_class="conjr-cover" css=".vc_custom_1482453330481{background-image: url(http://localhost/coolpad/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Product.Banner.Background.jpg?id=1531) !important;}"][vc_column][vc_row_inner content_placement="middle"][vc_column_inner el_class="content" width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="1505" img_size="" alignment="center"][vc_column_text el_class="actions"]\n<ul>\n 	<li style="text-align: center;"><a class="btn btn-light" href="#">Learn More</a></li>\n 	<li style="text-align: center;"><a class="btn btn-light" href="#">Buy Now</a></li>\n</ul>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text el_class="icons"]\n<ul>\n 	<li><img src="http://localhost/coolpad/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Asset-5.png" alt="8.0 M Front Camera with LED Flash" />8.0 M Front Camera with LED Flash</li>\n 	<li><img src="http://localhost/coolpad/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Asset-4.png" alt="Metal Body with 2.5D Touch Screen" />Metal Body with 2.5D Touch Screen</li>\n 	<li><img src="http://localhost/coolpad/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Asset-3.png" alt="5.0&quot; IPS HD Screen" />5.0" IPS HD Screen</li>\n 	<li><img src="http://localhost/coolpad/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Asset-2.png" alt="Fingerprint Sensor" />Fingerprint Sensor</li>\n</ul>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="1532" img_size="full" alignment="center" el_class="phone"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class="product-section-wrapper conjr-camera"][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner el_class="bottom" width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="1536" img_size="full" alignment="center" el_class="conjr-camera-phone website-phone"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class="vertical" width="1/2"][vc_column_text]\n<h4>Life in moments.</h4>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]13MP Rear Facing + 8MP Front Facing[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]With our 13MP rear facing and 8MP front facing cameras you can capture every important family moment or selfie with the best looking images. Cutting edge optical stabilization and noise reduction ensures that ever image you capture is sharp and crisp. Make every photo and video you take be the best.[/vc_column_text][vc_single_image image="1536" img_size="full" alignment="center" el_class="conjr-camera-phone mobile-phone"][vc_column_text el_class="icons"]\n<ul>\n 	<li><img src="http://localhost/coolpad/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/iso.png" alt="ISO" /></li>\n 	<li><img src="http://localhost/coolpad/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/shape.png" alt="Shape" /></li>\n 	<li><img src="http://localhost/coolpad/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/shape1.png" alt="Shutter" /></li>\n</ul>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class="product-section-wrapper conjr-performance" css=".vc_custom_1482311970689{background-color: #eeeeee !important;}"][vc_column][vc_column_text]\n<h4 style="text-align: center;">Fast is our middle name</h4>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]\n<p style="text-align: center;">With a Quad-core 1.0 GHz processor and 3GB of Ram, the coolpad conjr is built to handle multi-tasking your favorite games or apps. The phone doesn\'t just stop there, the conjr can also increase your productivity by reaching your emails, messages, and responses in a single touch</p>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_single_image image="1528" img_size="full" alignment="center" el_class="hidden-sm hidden-md hidden-lg"][vc_column_text el_class="features"]\n<ul>\n 	<li>\n<h5>3GB</h5>\nRam</li>\n 	<li>\n<h5>Snapdragon</h5>\nQualcomm</li>\n 	<li>\n<h5>Up to 64GB</h5>\nStorage</li>\n</ul>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_single_image image="1528" img_size="full" alignment="center" el_class="hidden-xs"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_custom_1482051704391{background-image: url(http://localhost/coolpad/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Elegant-Design.jpg?id=1412) !important;}" el_class="product-section-wrapper product-mobile-background-shift conjr-design"][vc_column][vc_column_text]\n<h4>Premium Crafted 2.5D Design</h4>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]What makes the coolpad conjr so beautiful is when the slight curves on the edges of the screen meet the brushed aluminum frame that surrounds it’s 5” display. Even with such a large display the phone rests so comfortably in your hand.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_custom_1482306891043{background-color: #eeeeee !important;}" el_class="product-section-wrapper conjr-technology"][vc_column][vc_row_inner css=".vc_custom_1482307416042{background-image: url(http://localhost/coolpad/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Dual-sim1.png?id=1413) !important;}" el_class="background"][vc_column_inner el_class="content"][vc_column_text]\n<h4>Dual Sim.</h4>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]The coolpad conjr has multi sim support for any international travelers and business people. Quickly switch between sim cards to adapt to your new location or back and forth from personal to business. No more hassle changing sim cards when you travel.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row content_placement="bottom" el_class="product-section-wrapper conjr-feature"][vc_column][vc_column_text]\n<h4 style="text-align: center;">Multi Finger Unlock.</h4>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]\n<p style="text-align: center;">Unlock your coolpad conjr with up to 5 differnt fingerprints. Immediate recogniction allows you to quick open apps and unlock your phone. Protect your personal information, family photos, banking, social media and so much more with a signature that is unique to you.</p>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_raw_html][/vc_raw_html][vc_single_image image="1414" img_size="full" alignment="center" el_class="mobile-phone"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row content_placement="middle" css=".vc_custom_1482051967803{background-color: #eeeeee !important;}" el_class="product-section-wrapper conjr-ui"][vc_column el_class="product-default-section"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_raw_html][/vc_raw_html][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_column_text]\n<h4>Coolpad UI 8.0</h4>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]\n<h5>An experience that understands you</h5>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]\n<h5>With the best screen capturing features in the market the coolpad conjr gives you the ability to screen record and multipage screenshots.</h5>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]\n<ol>\n 	<li>On Screen Recording</li>\n 	<li>Multi-Page Screenshots</li>\n 	<li>System one icon clean</li>\n 	<li>Easy File Transer</li>\n</ol>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'coolpad conjr', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1408-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-12-23 15:16:02', '2016-12-23 23:16:02', '', 1408, 'http://localhost/coolpad/1408-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
