-image: url(http://localhost/coolpad/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Dual-sim1.png?id=1413) !important;}" el_class="product-section-wrapper conjr-technology"][vc_column][vc_column_text el_class="title"]Dual Sim.[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text el_class="description"]The coolpad conjr has multi sim support for any international travelers and business people. Quickly switch between sim cards to adapt to your new location or back and forth from personal to business. No more hassle changing sim cards when you travel.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class="product-section-wrapper conjr-feature"][vc_column][ultimate_heading main_heading="Multi finger unlock."]Unlock your coolpad conjr with up to 5 differnt fingerprints. Immediate recogniction allows you to quick open apps and unlock your phone. Protect your personal information, family photos, banking, social media and so much more with a signature that is unique to you.[/ultimate_heading][vc_raw_html][/vc_raw_html][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row content_placement="middle" css=".vc_custom_1482051967803{background-color: #eeeeee !important;}" el_class="product-section-wrapper conjr-ui"][vc_column el_class="product-default-section"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_raw_html][/vc_raw_html][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][ultimate_heading main_heading="Coolpad UI 8.0" alignment="left"]An experience that understands you\r\n\r\nWith the best screen capturing features in the market the coolpad conjr gives you the ability to screen record and multipage screenshots.\r\n\r\n1. On Screen Recording\r\n2. Multi-Page Screenshots\r\n3. System one icon clean\r\n4. Easy File Transer[/ultimate_heading][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'coolpad conjr', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1408-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-12-19 22:45:01', '2016-12-20 06:45:01', '', 1408, 'http://localhost/coolpad/1408-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
